; directive-decimal-mark.test / commas.journal: a `decimal-mark ,`
; directive makes comma the decimal separator for undeclared commodities.
; Both legs are explicit so no counter-leg inference is needed (see the
; inferred-commodity-style GAP fixture for the elided-leg case).
decimal-mark ,
2021-05-01 YANDEX.PLUS
    Assets:Yandex            -199,00 RUB
    Expenses:Unknown:RUB      199,00 RUB
